data.title: Beautiful Places in Edinet District
data.meta_description: Beautiful Places in Edinet District - Free download as Powerpoint Presentation (.ppt / .pptx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document describes several beautiful natural areas located in Edinet District, Moldova. It discusses the La Castel landscape reservation featuring steep river valleys and caves. It also mentions the Little Switzerland reservation, known for its limestone cliffs up to 300 meters high. Finally, it provides details about the lavender field near Gordinești village and the Costești-Stânca accumulation lake, known for its crystal clear waters.
